title: Short Ghost and Horror Story Collection 021
creator: Various
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of the Short Ghost and Horror Story Collection 021. A collection of twenty stories featuring ghoulies, ghosties, long-leggedy beasties and things that go bump in the night. Expect shivers up your spine, the stench of human flesh, and the occasional touch of wonder. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
